{"tid":1424091,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"高官食哂花生","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:52.000Z","uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f737cecc90136a0f6cca7fecefd6bdc681b944d","tid":1424091,"uid":245041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"請睇哂全文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家林鄭放假<br />\n點解？因為佢用人民鬥人民<br />\n射哂個波卑狗<br />\n打狗係好重要 但依家高官就好似睇戲咁<br />\n睇我地每日圍狗屋 撚下狗<br />\n如果要對準政權 狗當然唔可以唔打 但點先可以再上一層樓令個運動對政府再受威脅d  <br />\n呢一點真係我地要再三諗下  當然唔係乜都唔做 但要重整下個方向<br />\n勇武係無盡頭 但依家就好似架車去到萬幾轉 卡住係樽頸位 欠一個轉波位<br />\n和理勇武缺一不可 但方向都係<br />\n呢一招真係好賤 應該點拆？？"},{"pid":"77b343dcf5f4180af0c732ff8b4786298bae0c6f","tid":1424091,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭放假係 fake news? 有無 fact check 過"},{"pid":"843f77e9da77b31a7561e3ee5893f2aeb0fabf78","tid":1424091,"uid":212973,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"77b343dcf5f4180af0c732ff8b4786298bae0c6f","tid":1424091,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:23:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭放假係 fake news? 有無 fact check 過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:28:52.000Z","msg":"fake news"}]}